headline: Mattel and WWE® Renew Global Licensing Partnership
summary: EL SEGUNDO, Calif., April 14, 2025--Mattel, Inc. (NASDAQ: MAT) and WWE, part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), today announced a multi-year extension to their global licensing agreement which sees Mattel continue to produce a wide range of WWE products including action figures and accessories, playsets, roleplay items, vehicles, and vehicle accessories.
